 alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76227\" //><button class=\"lightbox-trigger\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Agrandir l‘image\">\n			\n				\n			\n		</button><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Table des matières</figcaption>        <div data-wp-body=\"\" class=\"wp-lightbox-overlay zoom\" data-wp-effect=\"effects.core.image.initLightbox\">\n                <button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Fermer\" class=\"close-button\">\n                    \n                </button>\n                <div class=\"lightbox-image-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large responsive-image\" data-block-type=\"core\"><img data-id=\"76227\" src=\"\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76227\" //><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Table des matières</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div class=\"lightbox-image-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large enlarged-image\" data-block-type=\"core\"><img data-id=\"76227\" src=\"\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76227\" //><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Table des matières</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div class=\"scrim\" style=\"background-color: #fff\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure data-wp-context=\"{ &quot;core&quot;:\n				{ &quot;image&quot;:\n					{   &quot;imageLoaded&quot;: false,\n						&quot;initialized&quot;: false,\n						&quot;lightboxEnabled&quot;: false,\n						&quot;hideAnimationEnabled&quot;: false,\n						&quot;preloadInitialized&quot;: false,\n						&quot;lightboxAnimation&quot;: &quot;zoom&quot;,\n						&quot;imageUploadedSrc&quot;: &quot;https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/timetoread.png&quot;,\n						&quot;imageCurrentSrc&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n						&quot;targetWidth&quot;: &quot;701&quot;,\n						&quot;targetHeight&quot;: &quot;597&quot;,\n						&quot;scaleAttr&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n						&quot;dialogLabel&quot;: &quot;Image agrandie&quot;\n					}\n				}\n			}\" data-wp-interactive class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-lightbox-container\" data-block-type=\"core\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"701\" height=\"597\" data-wp-effect=\"effects.core.image.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-init=\"effects.core.image.initOriginImage\" data-id=\"76230\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/timetoread.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76230\" //><button class=\"lightbox-trigger\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Agrandir l‘image\">\n			\n				\n			\n		</button><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Temps de lecture</figcaption>        <div data-wp-body=\"\" class=\"wp-lightbox-overlay zoom\" data-wp-effect=\"effects.core.image.initLightbox\">\n                <button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Fermer\" class=\"close-button\">\n                    \n                </button>\n                <div class=\"lightbox-image-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large responsive-image\" data-block-type=\"core\"><img data-id=\"76230\" src=\"\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76230\" //><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Temps de lecture</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div class=\"lightbox-image-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large enlarged-image\" data-block-type=\"core\"><img data-id=\"76230\" src=\"\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-76230\" //><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Temps de lecture</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div class=\"scrim\" style=\"background-color: #fff\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n        </div></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ol data-block-type=\"core\"></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" data-block-type=\"core\">Dans cet épisode :</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol data-block-type=\"core\">\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Sécurité et performance :</strong> l&#8217;importance de la mise à jour pour la sécurité et l&#8217;efficacité de votre site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Gutenberg et ses innovations :</strong> explorez des fonctionnalités comme l&#8217;aperçu vignette des images, la nomination des groupes de blocs, et des options avancées pour la gestion des images, rendant la création de contenu plus intuitive.</li>\n\n\n\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Aspects techniques pour les professionnels :</strong> détails sur la typographie fluide, l&#8217;amélioration de l&#8217;API pour les révisions de post_metas, et l&#8217;introduction du block hook pour une personnalisation avancée. Ces éléments techniques offrent aux développeurs plus de flexibilité et de contrôle, optimisant ainsi le développement web et le SEO.</li>\n\n\n\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><strong>Les changements majeurs avec WordPress 6.4 :</strong> un aperçu des principales nouveautés et des fonctionnalités à venir, essentielles pour les entreprises.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ecoutez-le-podcast-sur\" data-block-type=\"core\">Ecoutez le podcast sur </h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/fr/podcast/woa-wordpress-on-air/id1482779414\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/apple-podcasts-e1571142591535.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66447\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/5rEMqG2cyoKYxpTTUAKSPp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/unknown.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66448\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-l